 />\n厚面皮d"},{"pid":"fae340b857d246e0fe2076e2e5d2c3c62a823b64","tid":82523,"uid":14206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>報左下個sem去瑞典exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問預左幾多錢去？物價如同？<br />\n點辛酸法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大約預十萬 物價睇下你買咩食咩 同煮喺咩城市 食開港女野all day breakfast就平過香港 但意粉pizza就好平 中國菜貴 買水貴 芝士牛奶平 同香港啲物價調返轉 未settle未開始煮飯 答唔到咁多 其中一樣辛酸以為可以識到外國朋友 但黎到你會發覺佢同你好似有層隔膜 <br />\n<br />\n利申：未身性格算外向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我仲諗住預7萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打有冇打算去附近國家玩？"},{"pid":"02aa26564b2f94c9ef589c5df9125af89a876a8a","tid":82523,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:59:33.000Z","msg":"瑞典exchange過一年留名"},{"pid":"40f5c33ad9b9a09f73056afad8af46accda05aee","tid":82523,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬"},{"pid":"95ed87135add2676d755cc3ff6222b8a71ae3ebe","tid":82523,"uid":50045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>報左下個sem去瑞典exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問預左幾多錢去？物價如同？<br />\n點辛酸法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大約預十萬 物價睇下你買咩食咩 同煮喺咩城市 食開港女野all day breakfast就平過香港 但意粉pizza就好平 中國菜貴 買水貴 芝士牛奶平 同香港啲物價調返轉 未settle未開始煮飯 答唔到咁多 其中一樣辛酸以為可以識到外國朋友 但黎到你會發覺佢同你好似有層隔膜 <br />\n<br />\n利申：未身性格算外向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我仲諗住預7萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打有冇打算去附近國家玩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果錢夠嘅 會去哂北歐國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f624c5070402ffd42f657a25b0e2a6abbcf9d07f","tid":82523,"uid":42009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎左第四日 日日新鮮日日甘</blockquote><br />\n有乜咁辛酸？"},{"pid":"e2004e07e3ebbfba25d1f74314e2166e1b3e0a1a","tid":82523,"uid":50045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞典exchange過一年留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪好快習慣到"},{"pid":"6d5c7ff4573232fb6c97246f4b86300d3082f34c","tid":82523,"uid":26093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實好多野都要時間，包括識朋友。你啱啱黎到唔慣就叫辛酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ff76f85d7cd4f285a1f6155d5a043d3dd267cd","tid":82523,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>瑞典exchange過一年留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪好快習慣到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好中意個種寧靜既芬圍，夏天去海邊行下睇下書，點行都唔會出汗。<br />\n<br />\n學識左自己買送煮野食<br />\n<br />\n記得第一日去到諗住食杯面，點知hostel連熱水都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />餓到仆街<br />\n<br />\n頭半年無乜朋友，但係都幾enjoy，仲有玩學校既管弦樂團<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d66d1b85e805b7e90a475a9048376263fb607bb","tid":82523,"uid":50045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>瑞典exchange過一年留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪好快習慣到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好中意個種寧靜既芬圍，夏天去海邊行下睇下書，點行都唔會出汗。<br />\n<br />\n學識左自己買送煮野食<br />\n<br />\n記得第一日去到諗住食杯面，點知hostel連熱水都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />餓到仆街<br />\n<br />\n頭半年無乜朋友，但係都幾enjoy，仲有玩學校既管弦樂團<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都幾鐘意依度嘅節奏 可能依度仲未有fd 獨來獨往有啲孤獨感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebc7d65915b077c87b71d471b5eba749a6957f7","tid":82523,"uid":6121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"瑞典治安係咪一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7343d77bb3e21facdc06ff4f32aae4a8af2ebc8","tid":82523,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞典治安係咪一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾人偷過相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住係蝻區就有啲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夜晚晚返去成班人係度圍住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d3000d2a043f72ae9869d6ef58e7c1805d8b60","tid":82523,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"10萬應該計埋玩啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c5ca0269302d97dea5416488e18d4781921518","tid":82523,"uid":50045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞典治安係咪一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n瑞典啲人比較冇咁亂 但去歐洲無論咩地方一定要打醒十二分精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8210844d5b7d2080753eb03a388d28c535cec6","tid":82523,"uid":50045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10萬應該計埋玩啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n包旅行啦當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla